---
import ProductLayout from "../../layouts/ProductLayout.astro";

const title = "技术架构 | 通用自动化测试平台";
const description = "技术架构页说明通用自动化测试平台的运行流程、系统分层、Product Bundle、Runtime、Plugin、Validation、Listener及当前支持边界。";
---

<ProductLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath="/test-platform/architecture/">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">技术架构</p>
    <h1>稳定内核负责执行与追溯，产品项目负责配置与扩展</h1>
    <p>架构页面向技术评估，不公开私有源码。文件名和模块名只作为开发者参考，页面主体使用公开抽象说明运行边界。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="runtime-flow" aria-labelledby="flow-diagram-title">
    <p class="section-kicker">客户运行流程图</p>
    <h2 id="flow-diagram-title">从选择产品到结果上报的执行路径</h2>
    <p class="diagram-hint">移动端可横向滑动查看完整图。</p>
    <svg class="diagram" viewBox="0 0 1120 260" role="img" aria-labelledby="flowSvgTitle flowSvgDesc">
      <title id="flowSvgTitle">客户运行流程图</title>
      <desc id="flowSvgDesc">Operator Product Selection 到 Product Bundle、Resource Initialization、Test Execution、Validation、Result Storage External Integration 的流程。</desc>
      <defs>
        <marker id="arrow" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="10" refX="8" refY="3" orient="auto">
          <path d="M0,0 L0,6 L9,3 z" fill="#0f766e"></path>
        </marker>
      </defs>
      <rect x="20" y="52" width="150" height="112" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="95" y="94" text-anchor="middle">Operator</text>
      <text x="95" y="122" text-anchor="middle">Product Selection</text>
      <line x1="170" y1="108" x2="215" y2="108" class="diagram-arrow"></line>
      <rect x="215" y="52" width="150" height="112" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="290" y="108" text-anchor="middle">Product Bundle</text>
      <line x1="365" y1="108" x2="410" y2="108" class="diagram-arrow"></line>
      <rect x="410" y="52" width="160" height="112" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="490" y="96" text-anchor="middle">Resource</text>
      <text x="490" y="124" text-anchor="middle">Initialization</text>
      <line x1="570" y1="108" x2="615" y2="108" class="diagram-arrow"></line>
      <rect x="615" y="52" width="150" height="112" rx="8" class="diagram-box accent"></rect>
      <text x="690" y="96" text-anchor="middle">Test</text>
      <text x="690" y="124" text-anchor="middle">Execution</text>
      <line x1="765" y1="108" x2="810" y2="108" class="diagram-arrow"></line>
      <rect x="810" y="52" width="130" height="112" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="875" y="108" text-anchor="middle">Validation</text>
      <line x1="940" y1="108" x2="985" y2="108" class="diagram-arrow"></line>
      <rect x="985" y="52" width="115" height="112" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="1042" y="94" text-anchor="middle">Result Storage</text>
      <text x="1042" y="122" text-anchor="middle">External Integration</text>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <section class="section tint" aria-labelledby="layer-diagram-title">
    <p class="section-kicker">开发人员系统分层图</p>
    <h2 id="layer-diagram-title">平台内核、插件边界和外部系统的关系</h2>
    <p class="diagram-hint">移动端可横向滑动查看完整图。</p>
    <svg class="diagram layer-diagram" viewBox="0 0 960 620" role="img" aria-labelledby="layerSvgTitle layerSvgDesc">
      <title id="layerSvgTitle">开发人员系统分层图</title>
      <desc id="layerSvgDesc">GUI Config Center、Main Scheduler、Runtime、Step Resource Listener Plugins、Validation Engine、Hardware Abstraction Storage External Systems 的分层架构。</desc>
      <defs>
        <marker id="arrowDown" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="10" refX="3" refY="8" orient="auto">
          <path d="M0,0 L6,0 L3,9 z" fill="#0f766e"></path>
        </marker>
      </defs>
      <rect x="260" y="28" width="440" height="64" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="480" y="68" text-anchor="middle">GUI / Config Center</text>
      <line x1="480" y1="92" x2="480" y2="130" class="diagram-arrow down"></line>
      <rect x="260" y="130" width="440" height="64" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="480" y="170" text-anchor="middle">Main Scheduler</text>
      <line x1="480" y1="194" x2="480" y2="232" class="diagram-arrow down"></line>
      <rect x="260" y="232" width="440" height="72" rx="8" class="diagram-box accent"></rect>
      <text x="480" y="276" text-anchor="middle">Runtime</text>
      <line x1="480" y1="304" x2="480" y2="338" class="diagram-arrow down"></line>
      <rect x="70" y="338" width="240" height="72" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="190" y="382" text-anchor="middle">Step Plugins</text>
      <rect x="360" y="338" width="240" height="72" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="480" y="382" text-anchor="middle">Resource Plugins</text>
      <rect x="650" y="338" width="240" height="72" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="770" y="382" text-anchor="middle">Listener Plugins</text>
      <line x1="480" y1="410" x2="480" y2="452" class="diagram-arrow down"></line>
      <rect x="260" y="452" width="440" height="64" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="480" y="492" text-anchor="middle">Validation Engine</text>
      <line x1="480" y1="516" x2="480" y2="554" class="diagram-arrow down"></line>
      <rect x="170" y="554" width="620" height="52" rx="8" class="diagram-box"></rect>
      <text x="480" y="586" text-anchor="middle">Hardware Abstraction / Storage / External Systems</text>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="architecture-notes">
    <p class="section-kicker">架构说明</p>
    <h2 id="architecture-notes">评估时应重点确认的边界</h2>
    <div class="grid two">
      <article class="card"><h3>稳定平台内核</h3><p>GUI、Main Scheduler、Runtime、Validation 和结果输出边界构成平台内核，负责加载配置、执行步骤、管理资源、记录结果。</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>产品项目配置</h3><p>产品项目主要配置 Product Bundle：设备资源、测试步骤、资源绑定、治具参数和 Listener 策略。</p></article>
      <article class="card" id="extension-boundary"><h3>插件扩展边界</h3><p>允许扩展测试步骤插件、硬件资源插件和结果监听器插件；外部协议和专用设备按项目实现。</p></article>
      <article class="card" id="data-flow"><h3>测试数据流</h3><p>测试开始后从输入标识和产品配置进入 Runtime，步骤采集测量值，Validation 生成判定，Listener 保存或上报结果。</p></article>
      <article class="card" id="resource-lifecycle"><h3>硬件资源生命周期</h3><p>资源在测试前按配置初始化，在执行中由步骤通过资源绑定调用，测试结束或异常时释放，避免流程直接操作底层硬件。</p></article>
      <article class="card" id="validation"><h3>判定规则层级</h3><p>判定规则在 Validation 层统一执行，步骤负责产生测量值和上下文，最终结果进入日志、结果库或外部系统。</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section dark" aria-labelledby="support-title">
    <p class="section-kicker">当前支持与不支持范围</p>
    <h2 id="support-title">明确边界比泛化承诺更重要</h2>
    <div class="grid two">
      <article class="plain-card"><h3>已确认</h3><p>Windows GUI、配置驱动、YAML 产品配置包、步骤/资源/监听器插件、本地结果和日志、SQLite、MQTT 或外部系统集成边界。</p></article>
      <article class="plain-card"><h3>待确认或按项目评估</h3><p>具体硬件型号、专用通信协议、MES 字段、云端认证方式、截图公开范围和版本号，需要结合项目资料确认。</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>
</ProductLayout>
